Trump was asked in an interview on Fox News whether he believed Obama was responsible for the town hall protests against Republicans this month. CAPE TOWN - US President Donald Trump says he believes former President Barack Obama has been behind leaks within his administration and demonstrations Republicans have faced across the country.Trump was asked in an interview on Fox News whether he believed Obama was responsible for the town hall protests against Republicans this month.Trump's administration has been beset by leaks to the media and he has continually rallied against those doing the leaking and the media since taking office.He has said the leaks are damaging to national security but also could not offer any evidence for his claim.